  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA307-kiḷavi">itu kuṟi nīṭa vāṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaḷait tōḻi vaṟpuṟuttiyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante encouraged HER who was unable to bear it when the meeting was delayed.</p>
        </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA307">
<l>            kavarpari neṭuntēr maṇiyu micaikkum</l>
<l>            peyarpaṭa viyaṅkiya viḷaiyaru molippar</l>
<l>            kaṭalāṭu viyaliṭaip pēraṇip polinta</l>
<l>            titalai yalku ṉalampā rāṭṭiya</l>
<l>            varumē tōḻi vārmaṇaṟ cērppa</l>
<l>            ṉiṟpaṭa vāṅkiya muḻavumutaṟ puṉṉai</l>
<l>            māvarai maṟaikam vammati pāṉāṭ</l>
<l>            pūviri kāṉaṟ puṇarkuṟi vantunam</l>
<l>            melliṇar naṟumpoḻiṟ kāṇātavaṉ</l>
<l>            ṉalla larumpaṭar kāṇkanāñ ciṟitē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The man from the coast of overflowing sands is coming, friend,</l>
<l rend="indent">in order to praise the goodness of [our] beauty-spotted hips</l>
<l rend="indent2">that glittered with big decorations in the wide place of playing in the sea,</l>
<l rend="indent3">for [his] youths being noisy, who travelled to achieve a name(?),</l>
<l rend="indent4">when also the bell of the long chariot with seizing motion sounds.</l>
<l>Come, let us hide behind the big trunk</l>
<l rend="indent">of the drum-based Puṉṉai tree, bent to touch the house(?).</l>
<l>Let us see a little of the severe affliction of unhappiness</l>
<l rend="indent">in him who does not see us in the grove fragrant with soft clusters,</l>
<l rend="indent">come to the sign of uniting in the seashore grove spread with flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent4">at midday.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
